Key Match Events: Ranger Suárez struck out the first five batters in his second start since he missed just more than a month with lower-back tightness
Orlando Arcia hit his 14th homer of the year
Sean Murphy connected for his eighth homer of the season
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Phillies are about a lock to reach the playoffs
The Braves are 5 games behind the Phillies in the NL East
Others: Reynaldo López won his second straight start and has seemingly rebounded from an 0-3 June
Bryce Harper doubled twice and singled but while wearing a black sleeve on his right arm
